extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #{title}!
  h2 What is Lab 2?
  p This Lab assignment involves the creation of a contacts database that features a few fields.
  p An autogenerated UUID, first name, last name, email, additional notes, and the date of creation.
  p The data is then saved to the file in contacts.json in the database folder in the root folder.
  p The database comes prepopulated with a single entry for John Smith as an example.
  p Feel free to add, edit, view, or delete as you see fit!
  p Click the button below to see it for yourself!
  a(href='/contacts') Enter the database!

  h3 Contact Info
  p If you have any questions or concerns reach out to me here on github!
